&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want a site like this? Check out &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack-starter" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;hugo-theme-stack-stater&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
